Camarillo.KCLU-FM: KCLU-FM is an NPR station covering Ventura County, California, at 88.3 (MHz) and Santa Barbara at 102.3 MHz and AM 1340 kHz. It's also heard on 89.7 in Santa Maria/Santa Ynez, and 92.1 in San Luis Obispo. It features NPR programming, local news, weather forecasts, and traffic conditions.
